'''關節穿刺術'''（Arthrocentesis，{{lang-el|arthros}}, 關節 + kentēsis, 穿刺）是使用[[注射器|注射器]]從[[关节囊|关节囊]]內抽取[[滑液|滑液]]的一種醫療處置<ref name="west">{{cite book|last1=West|first1=Sterling G.|title=Rheumatology Secrets|date=2002|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=1560534745|page=63|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=id4VID8BWtAC&dq=Arthrocentesis&source=gbs_navlinks_s|accessdate=8 November 2017|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511112930/https://books.google.com/books?id=id4VID8BWtAC&dq=Arthrocentesis&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。關節穿刺術常用於診斷[[痛风|痛风]]、[[关节炎|关节炎]]、以及滑液感染如[[敗血性關節炎|敗血性關節炎]]<ref name="west" />。

